text: Shizuko Sakashita (8 December 1933 - 17 May 1972) was a Japanese gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Japanese female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
